data.description: Move in ready 4 bed 2 bath property. Recently updated w a new kitchen & appliances, gas range, new wood floors, approx. 5 1/2 yr/old roof, 2 1/2 yr/old hot water heater, and 2 1/2 yr/old washer dryer; makes this home move in ready. It has a 2-car detached garage & 4 outdoor parking spaces plus RV parking. There's a cute little deck outside the kitchen/dining area for hangout & BBQ. The inside of the home has 4 bedrooms & 1.75 baths. The living room is on the main floor, +family room on lower level with a roomy laundry space! Fenced yard for privacy and all-around sprinkler system.
